08.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lily-allen-david-harbour@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lily-allen-david-harbour@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lily-allen-david-harbour@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-harbour">戴维·港（David Harbour）</a>结婚四年后已经分开。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/lily-allen-big-read-interview-2018-2334656"><em>NME</em> Big Read-莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）：“我正在掌握我的叙事”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该报告来自<a href="https://people.com/lily-allen-david-harbour-separate-after-4-years-marriage-exclusive-sources-8383999" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>人们</em></a>，他们写道，多个消息来源已经确认了他们的分裂。一位匿名消息人士补充说：“她的婚姻一直在崩溃，他们已经分裂了”。目前尚不清楚何时开始分离以及是否有和解的希望。</p><p>艾伦（Allen）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/stranger-things"><em>陌生人事物</em></a>演员戴维·港（David Harbour）在约会应用程序雷娜（Raya）会面后开始约会，并于2020年9月在拉斯维加斯亲密的拉斯维加斯仪式上结婚。</p><p>艾伦和港口的代表尚未确认报告。 </p><figure id="attachment_3822937" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822937" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822937" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lily-Allen@2000x1270.jpg" alt="莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）在2024年11月" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lily-Allen@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lily-Allen@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lily-Allen@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lily-Allen@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lily-Allen@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/L