后。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-foundation-announces-2-5million-donation-to-la-wildfire-relief-3828303">碧昂斯的Beygood基金会捐赠了250万美元，</a>以帮助救济工作。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-launches-fund-for-families-displaced-by-the-la-wildfires-3828081">巴黎·希尔顿（Paris Hilton）还为被大火流离失所的家庭开设了一项基金</a>，承诺要捐款100,000美元，最高可达100,000美元的捐款。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-spent-birthday-making-meals-for-families-hit-by-la-wildfires-3829226">戴夫·格罗尔（Dave Grohl）还为受到影响的家庭度过了生日</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/r-e-m-interpol-death-cab-for-cutie-featured-on-la-wildfire-recovery-album-good-music-to-lift-up-los-angeles-3834796">La Wildfire恢复专辑“ Good Music To Up Los Angeles”上的Cutie的REM，Interpol，Death Cab for Cutie</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
